The player starts with 100
health, the monster with 150 health (itâ€™s big!)
The player can choose to attack, heal, or run away.
If they attack, they deal between 10 - 15 damage to the monster.
If they heal, they regain 30 health, up to a maximum of 100.
If they run away, the game ends.
Athe playerâ€™s turn, if the monster is still alive, it deals 15 - 20 damage to theplayer.
The game continues until either the player or the monsterâ€™s health reaches 0 , or the player runs away.
